OL,3,CManchester Pub, famous for its musical
OL,4,Clinks is closing down
OL,6,FGranada Reports Correspondant Tim
OL,7,FScott has been speaking to some of the
OL,8,Fpeople who helped make Apsley Cottage
OL,9,Ffamous
OL,11,FA pub synonymous with famous bands and
OL,12,Fmusic fans has been forced to close -
OL,13,Fcausing an outcry from those who see
OL,14,Fit as a valuable piece of music
OL,15,Fhistory.
OL,17,FApsley Cottage, which sits behind the
OL,18,FManchester Apollo, first opened around
OL,19,F200 years ago and had become a firm
OL,20,Ffavourite for some of the world's most
OL,21,Fwell known musicians and comedians.
