OL,3,CManchester Pub, famous for its musical
OL,4,Clinks is closing down
OL,6,FMany including The Stone Roses and
OL,7,FOasis to more recent acts like The
OL,8,FBlossoms and Ricky Gervais have been
OL,9,Fspotted grabbing a quick pint, but the
OL,10,Fbrewery that owns the pub has now put
OL,11,Fit up for sale.
OL,13,F"I'm absolutely devastated, it was my
OL,14,Ffuture, we were planning on taking the
OL,15,Fpub over and were in talks with the
OL,16,Fbrewery," Ruth McAllister, the former
OL,17,Fmanager of the pub said.
