OL,6,F"I want to know why it was taken away
OL,7,Ffrom me when I was in talks with them
OL,8,Fand was basically told I was taking it
OL,9,Fover.
OL,11,F"For a pub that was making so much
OL,12,Fmoney, it doesn't make any sense."
OL,14,FA petition has now been launched by a
OL,15,Fmember of staff to try and save it,
OL,16,Fwith many famous faces giving it their
OL,17,Fbacking.
