OL,6,FStone Roses bassist Gary 'Mani'
OL,7,FMounfield said: "Having been here that
OL,8,Fmany times as a punter and as a
OL,9,Fprofessional musician, the way we let
OL,10,Fthe heritage go to rack and ruin in
OL,11,Fthis city is beyond me.
OL,13,F"Places like this should be cherished."
OL,15,FThe Apsley's walls are covered in
OL,16,Fphotos of people who have dropped in
OL,17,Ffor a post-concert drink, but the O-
OL,18,FMalleys say its true strength and
OL,19,Fpurpose was a community asset.
