OL,3,CManchester Pub, famous for its musical
OL,4,Clinks is closing down
OL,6,FJack O'Malley was landlord of the pub
OL,7,Fand first ran it with his late wife,
OL,8,FKathleen, who was much loved and
OL,9,Frespected by customers.
OL,11,FJack's grandson, Will Watts, said: "As
OL,12,Fmuch as we appreciate the stars that
OL,13,Fwent in the pub, that was never what
OL,14,Fthe pub was about, the pub wasn't a
OL,15,Fplace for stars to drink.
OL,17,F"It was a home, a hub for locals,
OL,18,Ffamily to enjoy themselves and for
OL,19,Fyears it has kept my grandad alive."
