OL,4,Clinks is closing down
OL,6,FThe building is more than 200 years
OL,7,Fold, and although the Apollo Theatre
OL,8,Fis a Grade II listed building, the pub
OL,9,Fis not.
OL,11,FThe Manchester Civic Society have
OL,12,Fapplied to have the building listed as
OL,13,Fa community asset, with the intention
OL,14,Fof eventually getting it fully listed.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Admiral Taverns
OL,17,Fsaid: "We worked closely with our
OL,18,Fformer licensee... to explore all
OL,19,Fpossible options for the pub's future.
OL,20,FHowever, we mutually agreed to part
OL,21,Fways.
